<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="acos" id="acos">acos</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">acos</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

acos()函数返回arg的反余弦，将会在[0, pi]范围内。arg应该在-1到1之间。如果arg出了此范围，acos()返回NAN并发出(raise)一个浮点异常。
</p>

<p>
C++ 同样提供了下列重载形式：

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">acos</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as acosf() in C99</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">acos</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as acosl() in C99</span></pre>
<p>
